LanguageData.RimMind.Storyteller.Prompt.TaskInstructi:
Only return the following JSON format, do not output anything else:
{"defName":"IncidentDef defName from candidate list","reason":"brief reason for selecting this event","announce":"announcement to player (max 20 words)","params":{"points_multiplier":0.6,"faction_hint":"Pirate","raid_strategy_hint":"ImmediateAttack"},"chain":{"chain_id":"pirate_threat_1","chain_step":1,"chain_total":3,"next_hint":"if the raid is repelled, pirates may send someone to negotiate or retaliate"}}
Where announce, params, and chain are optional fields.
